Android market fragmentation:
----------------------------
Android version usage:
http://developer.android.com/about/dashboards/index.html
--------------------
- I like using Nexus devices because they're designed for developers.
- It's easy to unlock their bootloaders and install a variety of Android versions on them.
- In the rest of this chapter I'll describe some useful strategies for managing this
  market fragmentation, including how to create alternative screen layouts and other
  resources for different sized screens.
- And how to create images of different sizes and resolutions for screens with a
  variety of pixel densities.
